        "ggVoREShrCJ_variantSelectionRequiredMessage": "Please select a variant to add product to cart",
        "ggd3njxJyN7_text": "60-day Guarantee",
        "ggCdVdus-lO_text": "<p>If it doesn’t live up to what we say, you’ve got 60 days to get every dollar back.<br>No hoops. No drama.</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_0": "<p>What’s inside?</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_1": "<p>Who’s it for?</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_2": "<p>How long does it last?</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_3": "<p>How to use it</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_4": "<p>How much do I save?</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_5": "<p>Can I buy them separately?</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_6": "<p>60-Day Guarantee</p>",
        "ggKZrkCgfQz_text": "<p>• 1x Face Cleanser — 100ml<br>• 1x Eye Cream — 15ml<br>• 1x Night Face Cream — 50ml</p>",
        "ggLuQ0nuQN8_text": "<p>Men 40+ who want to look sharp — not tired.</p><p>If you want to:<br>• Stay ahead of wrinkles<br>• Cut down under-eye bags and dark circles<br>• Take care of your skin without overthinking it</p><p>This is the full setup. Morning and night. No guesswork.</p>",
        "ggR8kqovO2L_text": "<p>With daily use:</p><p>Face Cleanser — about 2 months<br>Eye Cream — about 1 month<br>Night Cream — about 1 month</p>",
        "ggFipoBsWwP_text": "<p>Morning</p><p><strong>Cleanser</strong> — massage onto wet face. Rinse.<br><strong>Eye Cream</strong> — apply under eyes with the metal applicator.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Night</p><p><strong>Cleanser</strong> — washes off dirt, oil, and the day.<br><strong>Eye Cream</strong> — under eyes again.<br><strong>Night Cream</strong> — 1–2 pumps on face and neck.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Pro tip:</strong><br>At night, wait a few seconds after the eye cream before using the night cream. Helps it absorb better.</p>",
        "ggNgskm7d42_text": "<p>The kit is €69.99 instead of €90.</p><p>You save €20.</p><p>Simple.</p>",
        "ggg59nFYXJE_text": "<p>Yes.</p><p>But the kit costs less — and gives you the full day + night routine in one shot.</p>",
        "ggWWrnyOmWZ_text": "<p>Try it for 60 days.</p><p>If you don’t see the results you expected, email us.<br>You get 100% of your money back.</p><p>We stand behind it.</p>"
      }
    },
