        "gg5r67GKkA8_childItem_7": "<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Can I pay on delivery?</span></p>",
        "ggKeQeBypCw_text": "<p>Right now? No.</p><p>SerlinoLab is available <strong>online only</strong> —<br>on our official website and on Amazon.</p><p>If you see it somewhere else, there’s a good chance it’s not the real thing.</p><p>Pharmacy availability is coming soon.</p><p>Own a pharmacy?<br>Reach out on WhatsApp or email info@serlinolab.it.</p>",
        "ggE2a9V-meS_text": "<p>• 1x Face Cleanser — 100ml<br>• 1x Eye Cream — 15ml<br>• 1x Night Face Cream — 50ml</p><p>Everything you need.</p>",
        "ggBr_m71saN_text": "<p>Men 40+ who want to stay ahead of the game.</p><p>If you want to:<br>• Stay on top of wrinkles<br>• Cut down under-eye bags<br>• Protect your skin during the day<br>• Repair it at night</p><p>This setup covers it.</p><p>No shortcuts. No fluff.</p>",
        "gg2xFSx-IzP_text": "<p>With daily use:</p><p>Cleanser — about 2 months<br>Eye Cream — about 1 month<br>Night Cream — about 1 month</p>",
        "ggzn9yZbmxc_text": "<p>Morning</p><p><strong>Cleanser</strong> — massage onto wet face. Rinse.<br><strong>Eye Cream</strong> — apply under eyes using the metal applicator.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Night</p><p><strong>Cleanser</strong> — washes off dirt, oil, and the day.<br><strong>Eye Cream</strong> — under eyes again.<br><strong>Night Cream</strong> — 1–2 pumps on face and neck.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Pro tip:<br>At night, wait a few seconds after the eye cream before applying the night cream.<br>Helps it absorb better.</p>",
        "gglFYYGZwgb_text": "<p>The kit is €69.99 instead of €90.</p><p>You save €20.</p>",
        "ggNOYtAGI-h_text": "<p>Yes.</p><p>But the kit saves you money — and gives you the full morning + night routine in one shot.</p>",
        "ggSlD4p6ePO_text": "<p>Yes.</p><p>Your order shows up in 24–48 hours.<br>Pay cash when it arrives.</p>"
