    "gp_section_609155102188307104": {
      "type": "gp-section-609155102188307104",
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "56c85431de06a2e846452ad912d8507a3b55c31f9b45f017a335d11e54169dae_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggd_h9m0Ttw_text": "<span style=\"color:#17162E;\">Your Routine. 3 Minutes a Day</span>",
        "ggsgaIY_jCQ_text": "<p>That’s it. No 12-step nonsense</p>",
        "gg3Lg-iTOOA_text": "<p>Face Cleanser</p>",
        "ggI1h1C4iQv_text": "<p>Morning + night. Massage onto a wet face. Rinse it off. Gets rid of dirt, oil, and whatever the day threw at you.</p>",
        "gg3FlbQHhtI_text": "<p>Eye Cream</p>",
        "ggv237rnjlO_text": "<p>Morning + night. Apply directly under your eyes. Quick swipe. Done. Helps with bags. Helps with dark circles. Makes you look less tired.</p>",
        "gg6kpolwlh1_text": "<p>Night Face Cream</p>",
        "gg7K0cdmUSt_text": "<p>Night only. 1–2 pumps on face and neck. Let it absorb. Works while you sleep.</p>",
        "ggO3tk5n4JG_text": "<p>2–8 drops in your palm</p>",
        "ggQs1EC0vxl_text": "<p>(More drops = darker color)</p>",
        "ggL9hxzsbiZ_text": "<p>Rub it in</p>",
        "ggk6SeXLa4T_text": "<p>Face clean. Face dry</p>",
        "ggfVDP-3KJn_text": "<p>Wash your hands</p>",
        "ggxoVmfJ5n8_text": "<p>Right away</p>",
        "ggbQEC9Z_If_childItem_0": "<p>Pro Tip</p>",
        "ggz72ubszUw_text": "<p>Use the cleanser before shaving. It softens your skin and beard so the razor glides easier. Less irritation. Cleaner shave.<br>Three minutes. Twice a day. No excuses.</p>"
      }
    },
